column5: She's Hungarian. (Everyone is Hungarian at my schools.)
I knew a weird girl from school who was obsessed with Hitler.
Same, when the time is 11:11 or 22:22 I always make a wish.

My  teacher wrote to my class that we have to send her our homework on google classroom UNTIL TUESDAY MIDNIGHT. I sent it to her on Tuesday afternoon and when I entered in the classroom it was already classified, and my points were  0/100 . I don't undersand why did she classify it if she wrote it there we have time until midnight to send it. I didn't saw any bad grades in the diary, I guess she found my homework after.

Similar thing happened to me. I met a guy in my dream who was familiar to me but I didn't met him in real life. We became friends. He appeared in more dreams and he recognized me.

I think this thing is common for people. I've seen others posting here things like this happened to them. Somebody said they saw the person after they dreamed of them.

When I dream about my school it always has much more floors, classrooms, and hallways. Sometimes my high school building also includes my primary school inside of it. I keep searching for my classroom but I can't find it.

A week ago I had a dream where I was walking home on the road at night alone, I heard wolf howling, then 2 vultures flew on the sky and they were talking about me. Then I sat on a floating sofa with some other people and 2 parrots in the middle of the road. The sofa flew up to the sky and we were looking at the shooting stars, I wished the same thing everytime I saw one. A big floating paper appeared above us with my Scorpio star sign written on it, but I couldn't read what was written under it because the paper dissapeared. A floating diary appeared too and i grabbed it and took it home so it won't dissapear. I woke up but I was still in the dream and I told this dream to somebody and again i woke up and I was still dreaming and again i told it to somebody. Then I woke up in the real life.

The feeling of the dream gave me a good mood for the day.
Yes I have dreams like these.
No, they didn't find out. I never told them and they weren't assuming it was me.

In 7th grade when I was walking to school I stepped in dog poop. I didn't told it anyone. In the class me and other girls were talking and one of them (I call her G) smelled the dog poop, but she didn't know it was coming from my boots. 

There was a girl in class who never showers, never washed her clothes, and never brushed her hair, and smelled every day very bad and she got confronted by others for that before, but she just doesn't care about hygiene (lets call her P).

So the girl who sensed the poop she immidiately said that ''Where is this awful smell coming from? I think it's from P hahahaha''.  P's face got red.

In the last class we had that day I was sitting in front of G, then she smelled the dog poop again and looked at P who was sitting in the other side of the class, meters away. And then G said "OMG I can smell P's awful smell from here!". P is got red again.
This happened to me so many times.
Days ago when I didn't feel well, I had a dream I met Norman Reedus in a shop and he hugged me. It made me feel so much better. But most of the time celebrity crushes appear randomly in my dreams.

" This popular youtuber claimed to be trans-"

At that moment I already knew who were you talking about. I hate her so much, she made me so angry. I think she's just trying to get the attention on youtube for views.
Yes. At least i was able to sleep till 10:30 insead of 5:30.

I had only toxic friends before.

It's hard to find the right people who are real friends.
I'm at the end of the last year of school, I'm not gonna see them after that THANK GOD!

Before I go in the school, people are already standing there and as I walk by they are staring at me they even say some stupid stuff about me, they think I can't hear them. I have only toxic friends and they are also the toxic friends of each other because they are always talk bad stuff about each other in front of me, but they hang out a lot. They criticize me for not beng that social, but when I go up to them to hang out at school they just staring and questioning why did I go up to them, why am i there?, they don't want me to hear the topic. Pure anxiety!!!   (The school is on lockdown, so at least I'm free from them for a while.)
Do you know what is even worse? When a couple is standing next to you and they start to kiss loudly.

Similar thing happening to me. I saw a guy in my dreams, he appeared there more times and he an I are recognised each other in those dreams. I never saw him in real life but he's familiar to me, even at the first time I met him in the dream.

One time toddlers and kids ran up to one of my relative's huge present and they ripped apart the nicely done paper on it into little pieces, the grass was full of it, then they pushed the whole box on the side. It's a miracle it didn't break, it was a huge alcohol making machine. Their parents didn't tell the kids to stop, everyone was like wtf.
9 is my lucky number and I doubled it because why not.

I feel that when i'm in public. I feel like they are judging me all the time and when they are laughing i think they are making fun of me. I was born as a girl but i want to be a man but i can't transition yet, but i look already very manly.

I'm trying to go step by step, caring less about the rituals. Have that thought: "Do these rituals make a good change in the future with my life? They just take away more time. If I don't do the rituals nothing is gonna change, i'm just gonna have more freetime in my life."
I feel something. Like a big change is about to happen or something...

I have this kind of thing. I can't go in my room to my laptop without being clean. I water my hair a little and dry it after school so i won't take the germs in my room. I wash my hands a lot, after everything. There are relatives who don't wash hands after anything and they touch everything in our house so i have to be careful...
Believe me they are interesting, i wish i had it instead of what i have LOL
I heard about those products in a cringe compilation. It must be gross to use those in my opinion. It will be full of stuff after every time.
Yes I'm self-aware when I have SP. One time I was so calm i even slept back because i was like oh it's just a SP i'm going to sleep back, what else can i do(?

Yes, same with me. I hate alcohol, people in my area always telling me to drink, even when I was underage they were already giving it to me but I didn't drink it because I hate it and i'm gonna hate it forever. Months ago I drank 2 smaller glass of Liqueur and i hated it so much, even that tastes so bad, and the burning feeling is so annoying and people are paying for this.

I was forced to go on one of my relatives 70th birthday and i didn't wanted to drink alcohol and they wanted me to feel guilty for it. They said "Oh so you are gonna drink on her 80th one?, like she can live for that long". OMG I'm not gonna drink alcohol in my life. NEVER!  I'm going to be on the other side of the Earth in 4 years so they cannot expect me to stay around them 10 years more, that would be hell.

(There are millions of reasons too, why i wanna get away from them as fast as possible.)
I know somebody who lent her eyeliner to a stranger woman. When she got it back and used it, her eyes started hurting, burning and tearing from it.

The step-grandpa in the family is a sexist. He calls every women 'pussy'. When he and his 2 yr old grandson was in the dining room with female relatives and me, he said to his grandson: 'It must be awful to poor little you, you have to be in the same room with these pussies.' 

(I wanted to break his neck, honestly.)

Same dude. I cannot say my feelings out loud because people in my area are find me crazy and weird, and they are hating on me because i'm different from them. If I dare to just stand up for myself and tell my opinion or anything, they would just look down on me, calling me selfish, and they are playing the victim, and they are whining to me because they have to hear what i'm saying to them.

Yes, they go too fast. When i was in primary school 11 year old girls drank alcohol, one of them had her own alcohol-shelf in her room, and they need 2 boxes of cigarettes every day. They already went to parties in revealing clothes, they tryed to hook up with people, getting drunk. They also had every kind of piercings on their body at 13. There are girls who had lots of ex-BFs at 12. Some of them got pregnant. 

I'm not like these people.

I hate bees and wasps too. When i see them fly near me i start to panic and get away from them as far as possible. I hate it when people are telling me to 'don't be scared, and let it fly on you, it won't stung you.' BUT I WILL NEVER LET THEM FLY ON ME!!!

When i was 16 i was at a culture-booth, sitting there, a small kid pointed at me, asked loudly her mother 'Is that a man or a woman???' Her mother dragged her away because she was ashamed maybe...

I was born as a girl but i want to be a man. I wish I was a man, I can't wait to transition.
I have a strong jawline, manly face,nose,eyes,eyebrows, NO feminine idoms, I'm tall, thin, and I don't wear girly clothes. I had a huge pony tail but she was still questioning if I was a man.

(If i would cut off my hair i swear I would really look like a man.)

Same, I hate it too. I know  some people who do that. She just randomly touch my shoulder while she talks to me. (I know that she never washes her hands after peeing at school, so it's extra gross.)

I'm only okay with hot men, and very close people to me who are being touchy.
